title: Slipstream
description:
5 x 30 mins

Sci Fi meets thriller in this Simon Bovey 5 parter.

It is 1945 and Nazi Germany appears to have a fantastic new fighter. The allies are determined to get their hands on it, thus an advance party is sent in to capture it. They find the craft and its pilot, to discover that the craft appears to be powered by thought alone - and is not of human manufacture.....

Enjoyable nonsense.
